node.text:
Ugly? Heh.. it’s something you feel when you’re unable to look through your own self. With eyes wide open but soul too numb to feel or sense what’s wrong and what’s right. 
You’re made up of a hundred shades and re-mixing them would probably make a better picture. 
Just let the light in for you to see and some air to wake you up. 
Yet eyes don’t see what bleeds inside of you.
The colours are individually all lovely❣️
.
.

I’m way too good at goodbyes..
